紙,(避免隔水加熱時水份會流進模型裡)接著倒入麵糊,用橡皮刮刀將麵糊表面刮平整。 烤箱先預熱170度c備用。烤模放入大烤盤裡,注入約2cm高度的熱水,放進烤箱以170度c烘烤40分鐘,接著再用160度c繼續烘烤10-15分鐘。搖動模型時,蛋糕表面會像布丁般緩緩搖動的半熟狀態,即代表完成。請依各家烤箱的不同,烘烤時間可做調整。"},{"pid":"97ed6d2468f9920847db4983a202130cf136bff2","tid":137714,"uid":35712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:03:11.000Z","msg":"死窮鬼"},{"pid":"3589b8c9dbc3dcbb29aa3cd519fb8b19ed695f60","tid":137714,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"937586a69f2c0c2bb57b48de7acdd6fb1667806c","tid":137714,"uid":77820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:13:17.000Z","msg":"你好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cad5e168878717d8efa19f8b7b9fd2cd92bb7bcb","tid":137714,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:15:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解要搵我同你食野<br />\n你無朋友咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095f1b4eb9eba9b290cc906b19327686990a0e2d","tid":137714,"uid":11156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:15:56.000Z","msg":"你都冇錢學咩人去旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11c646910688d2d52efe8f1dbe26b4e469a8bf54","tid":137714,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點解你可以一啲上進心都無架？</blockquote><br />\n呢個真係好難聽 點答都仆街死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99929fa34d0f8bfb3d9b03dcf8deba71a9e58612","tid":137714,"uid":33972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:24:30.000Z","msg":"呢句說話仲難聽過粗口"},{"pid":"fc2c95efa57813217985fc3065afa3c14971b014","tid":137714,"uid":9428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死矮婆</blockquote><br />\n今年有五